{"tid":865712,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[以為自己係apple]華為 Mate 20 不支援 microSD！只支援自家研發記憶卡 NM Card !","createTime":"2018-10-17T09:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T16:29:35.000Z","uid":10717,"like":10,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe687caf0e53350ca72f2708587e4f4b2ab75da","tid":865712,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"昨晚在倫敦舉行的華為發佈會，公佈了 Mate 20、Mate 20 Pro、Mate 20 RS 和 Mate 20X 手機，這批手機有不少賣點，例如 Leica 認證的三鏡頭相機、逆向無線充電、石墨薄膜散熱等，其實華為還藉著昨日的發佈會宣佈，新發表的 Mate 20 系列手機，通通只支援 NM Card 作為記憶擴充。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMWEx2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMWEx2d.jpg&h=9a57a686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為 Mate 20 不支援 microSD！全新記憶卡 NM Card 發表<br />\n<br />\n以 NM Card 取代我們常見的 microSD 究竟是好是壞？NM Card 全名為 Nano Memory Card，是華為研發的全新記憶儲存卡，功能和 microSD 相若但體積細 45%，外形和尺寸跟 nano SIM 一樣，可以用於 Mate 20 系列的 Dual SIM 托盤，用戶可以選擇兩張 nano SIM 或一張 nano SIM 加一張 NM Card。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GKVQOX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GKVQOX.jpg&h=3e52aad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為 Mate 20 不支援 microSD！全新記憶卡 NM Card 發表<br />\n<br />\n華為暫時未有透露 NM Card 的詳細規格資料，在昨日的發佈會中，見到 NM Card 的最大容量為 256GB，速度為 90MB/s。暫時亦未公佈 NM Card 的售價和銷售點，是否有其他廠商支援亦未有透露，似乎 Mate 20 手機的準買家要在買機時先估計自己需要的容量，因為透過記憶卡擴充的方案或者會比使用 microSD 麻煩，甚至昂貴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以為自己係apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8464c55365774b0d6e3438182ff5148b89eb02fc","tid":865712,"uid":164092,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"90MB/S，仲慢過SD CARD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeee5443e5d154cea6c3261b2035d393e8722799","tid":865712,"uid":25794,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:10:43.000Z","msg":"可以參考下SONY <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d48b3f9a975f5e816ae60648169768fa58fbd02","tid":865712,"uid":50267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"學ps vita先真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb41f6addb119ac92aa82972db9dbc79ca987aff","tid":865712,"uid":5220,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8464c55365774b0d6e3438182ff5148b89eb02fc","tid":865712,"uid":164092,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:09:08.000Z","msg":"90MB/S，仲慢過SD CARD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"冇同其他記憶卡大廠合作<br />\n我覺得係照搬SD卡UHS I卡標準整出黎，一樣都係最高9X MB/s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f8aa3e5bac89a4cbc600ec67a28fb016de0e02","tid":865712,"uid":59499,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"班打手又會話唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc32fb3dd94492300e994dc43262e6729b5c2be","tid":865712,"uid":179467,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"罪大的MS同PS Vita記憶卡: 支那總要重複人類的錯誤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/d